headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Explore Your Inner Street Artist: LS Tags
content:
Send a message to Big Business while unleashing your inner street artist.

Find spray cans around Los Santos to unlock this new collectible, then search for corporate posters and tag five in a day to unlock an exclusive reward.

Keep track of how many posters youâ€™ve tagged each day in the Collectibles section of the Interaction Menu.
